A place for me to store systems wide DotFiles for all my accounts.

PapaInstaller info:
    WORKS ONLY ON DEBIAN SYSTEMS
    PapaInstaller -d
        installs paparazzi from the default repo(git@gitub.com:paparazzi/paparazzi.git)
    PapaInstaller -c
        intstalls paparazzi from CnuUasLab repo(git@github.com:cnuuaslab/paparazzi.com)

mover info:
    moves all the files/ssh keys to their respective locations
